Store completed interview transcripts here.  Specifically, store them in a
subdirecotry named for the department in which the interview was held.  Use the
two to four character directory name, as they appear in the campus catalog at
http://catalog.calpoly.edu/2011cat/course_descr2011.html.

See the 308 milestone 2 writeup
for the naming conventions of transcript files.  The specific URL is

    http://users.csc.calpoly.edu/~gfisher/classes/308/handouts/milestone2.html#transcript-file

Store audio recordings in a DEPT./audio subdirectory.  See the preceding URL
for the audio file naming conventions.
